<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邮局的老奶奶对鲍比、菲利斯和彼得说：“你们都是好孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29144</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是一辆闲置的婴儿车，本来是给我的孙子买的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但我们在他六个月的时候失去了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以我想把这个送给帕克斯夫人的小宝宝。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菲利斯抱住老奶奶说：“帕克斯会非常开心的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把所有的礼物都放进婴儿车，然后来到帕克斯家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60022</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>花园很整洁，窗台上放着一罐雏菊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60022</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比敲了敲门。帕克斯夫人走了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们带了一些生日礼物给帕克斯。”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把礼物拿出来的时候，帕克斯夫人非常惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她突然哭了起来，大家都吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请别这样！”孩子们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得着急地问：“您这是怎么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帕克斯夫人还在轻轻地哭泣，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的孩子们也站在大门口，不过有些难为情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都很尴尬。菲利斯和鲍比拍着帕克斯夫人的后背。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她慢慢停止哭泣说：“帕克斯从来没有过过这样的生日，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>连他小时候也没有。你们真是好孩子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帕克斯夫人把面包和醋栗放在盘子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们躲在洗衣房里，然后给帕克斯一个惊喜吧。”鲍比小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们跑进洗衣房，但没有时间关门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136544</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们只好把帕克斯的孩子们挡在前面，大家挤在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我回来了！”帕克斯喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“漂亮吗？这是为你的生日准备的茶叶。”帕克斯夫人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>外面传来亲吻的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里怎么有一辆婴儿车？”帕克斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些是什么？你从哪里……？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帕克斯夫人小声说了些什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不管。”帕克斯生气地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这几年我们都过得很好，我才不要这些施舍！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘘！”帕克斯夫人说，“孩子们会听到的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“刚好，我也要问问他们！”他大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“出来！告诉我为什么这么做！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我说过我需要什么吗？我为什么要收下这些施舍？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帕克斯重重地坐到椅子上，皱着眉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……”菲利斯说，“我以为你会很高兴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我保证，我再也不会这样做了。”她哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们并不想让您生气。”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可你们的做法让我很生气！”帕克斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但这些礼物不全是我们送的，还有其他人的心意。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是谁去要的？”帕克斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我们。”菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以是你们告诉所有的邻居，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们很穷，需要施舍？”帕克斯问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们可以带着婴儿车和礼物回去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他转过椅子，不再看孩子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比突然说话了：“是我们大家想要送给你生日礼物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帕克斯慢慢地把椅子转向孩子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看上去没有那么生气了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270879</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比继续小声说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270879</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“医生说：‘我很愿意送帕克斯礼物，他总是按时付钱。’”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比的声音稍微大了一点：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“食品店的主人说：‘帕克斯工作很努力。’</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邮局的老奶奶说你总是——”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别说了。”帕克斯突然说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我收回我刚才说过的话，是我误会你们了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我很开心……不仅因为礼物，还因为邻居们的善意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这才是最好的礼物，对吗，内尔？”他的妻子点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310481</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帕克斯看着孩子们：“你们要留下来喝茶吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然要啊！”孩子们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>